CONNECTORID, L.L.C.
v.
FMI PRODS., L.L.C. 2019-0876 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 20, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

APPEAL NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW.

Donnelly, J., concurs because the extreme brevity of the accelerated-calendar judgment entry makes it impossible to discern what arguments were even raised below, let alone whether they might address an issue of public or great general interest.
